name: Round Tiger Robot
description:
With lines and circles, we can make what we want. Like this tiger artwork. If the face of a tiger is like this, will we be afraid? Or are we going to hug it because it's cute?
We have to take care of it, because the population is getting less and less on this earth. It will never be replaced by a robot. This is a message from the REAL WOLRD, not the METAVERSE
